  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"DyCIgnAH\">如果你所说的自卑软弱，不敢社交，是怕别人说你娘，那也许需要更正一下对娘的认知。如果不是的话，其实不少人也有这些问题，那就是多多提升自己，从心底里认可喜欢自己，再锻炼社交技能就可以了。</p><p data-pid=\"kwsT3Pxt\">娘其实不是贬义词，我们以前不都喊母亲叫娘吗？<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=415908534&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%90%B4%E9%9D%92%E5%B3%B0&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">吴青峰<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>以前也被说娘，他说女性化特质有什么不好，关键是有没有担当。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f11b59feffeb603a411d15ac7b091362_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"3102\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-9c94cdb5312b5426e7716d123ae5eb5c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9ad0a2d9921fc48ef421890a1cfc32f7_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f11b59feffeb603a411d15ac7b091362_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='3102'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"3102\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-9c94cdb5312b5426e7716d123ae5eb5c\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-9ad0a2d9921fc48ef421890a1cfc32f7_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f11b59feffeb603a411d15ac7b091362_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f11b59feffeb603a411d15ac7b091362_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-01cea2d77fbce1f0aa85ed911e974b32_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2340\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-aafbe34c5ecf0695acb182a1edb06a85\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-19e8e895ccd36c21b467779eba17f8e3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-01cea2d77fbce1f0aa85ed911e974b32_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='1080' height='2340'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"2340\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-aafbe34c5ecf0695acb182a1edb06a85\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-19e8e895ccd36c21b467779eba17f8e3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-01cea2d77fbce1f0aa85ed911e974b32_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-01cea2d77fbce1f0aa85ed911e974b32_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-65548f26dfe25c939f57b64f179c3c31_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"690\" data-rawheight=\"2146\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-8d1a365a391b382ea0d9cea6a6c73063\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c7a9a786af5b2c59275c22c999718c39_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"690\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-65548f26dfe25c939f57b64f179c3c31_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='690' height='2146'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"690\" data-rawheight=\"2146\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-8d1a365a391b382ea0d9cea6a6c73063\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c7a9a786af5b2c59275c22c999718c39_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"690\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-65548f26dfe25c939f57b64f179c3c31_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-65548f26dfe25c939f57b64f179c3c31_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"B5csBVEV\">其次，女生要淑女，男生要有男子汉气概，本身就是刻板印象，所谓男性气质<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=415908534&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%A5%B3%E6%80%A7%E6%B0%94%E8%B4%A8&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">女性气质<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，也是社会后天的规训，你大可以不遵守，其实还蛮酷的。“在个性差异的意义上接受每个人，而不是在性别的差异上来规范每个人。 ”你自己舒服喜欢就好了</p><p data-pid=\"_r20QDTN\">蔡依林的《玫瑰少年》讲的是台湾男孩<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=415908534&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%8F%B6%E6%B0%B8%E5%BF%97&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">叶永志<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>因为女性化被男同学扒裤子，被骂娘娘腔，最后离开了这个世界。他只是长相清秀，可爱温柔，懂事地帮妈妈按摩做家务。老师让他妈妈去看<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=415908534&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%8C%BB%E7%94%9F&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">心理医生<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，医生说：你儿子非常健康，如果觉得他这样不正常的人，他本身就不正常。</p><p data-pid=\"9IO5ennP\">叶永志没有错，你也没有错，错的是这个社会的偏见太深。</p><p data-pid=\"gQ7aHI86\">我高中也有个女性化的男生，喜欢和女生一起玩，看<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=415908534&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%81%B6%E5%83%8F%E5%89%A7&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">偶像剧<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>，可是他人很好，后来还考上了<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=415908534&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E5%86%9B%E5%8C%BB%E5%A4%A7%E5%AD%A6&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">军医大学<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。至于恋爱，不体贴的直男也不受欢迎啊，我就知道有女生会喜欢你这类型。良性的恋爱关系对谁来说都不容易，要找到合适的喜欢的才行。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e62c1ba65ec0e7320dd2b585605b46ed_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"690\" data-rawheight=\"1563\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-36e4fc95b4ed92c2eccfa3bb070a7523\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5bc3201c123f0bce252f0e7b5d49b027_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"690\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e62c1ba65ec0e7320dd2b585605b46ed_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='690' height='1563'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"690\" data-rawheight=\"1563\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-36e4fc95b4ed92c2eccfa3bb070a7523\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5bc3201c123f0bce252f0e7b5d49b027_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" wi